вЂ‹High Traffic Test (Task 2): Initiated three simultaneous ping streams (PC1в†’PC6, PC2в†’PC5, PC3в†’PC4) to induce congestion in the shared link.  
вЂ‹Observations
вЂ‹(Replace this section with your specific 3вЂ“5 points comparing the results)
вЂ‹Example Point 1: During the baseline test, the ping response time was consistently low with zero packet loss.
